title: 2012 NHRA Auto-Plus Keystone Nationals partial ESPNl
description:
2012 NHRA Auto-Plus Keystone Nationals at Maple Grove Pa, -NOT- the complete race. From an ESPN broadcast that got to me thru a pal's analog recorder (Std def.)- Sunday and what he could get on Monday...

    The .avi file looked rather poor at 1.2Gb so I re-ripped it as 1.7Gb. Expect few seeders and reduced seeding from me after the get-go. Please help out by replacing what you get, more if possible.

1.)Sunday elimination TF,FC,PS round 1, TF round 2 only(avi)

2.)Saturday + Monday's TAD, TAFC only (alcohol)- round 1,2, semifinals and finals.(mp4)
